get this straight.

00:44:30.580 --> 00:44:32.670
You want us to give them
their fentanyl back?

00:44:32.844 --> 00:44:34.715
Just give 'em what they want.

00:44:34.889 --> 00:44:36.804
All right,
when they return the boys,

00:44:36.978 --> 00:44:39.348
