with somebody else, asshole.

00:47:58.179 --> 00:47:59.789
Bullshit! Where are they?

00:47:59.964 --> 00:48:01.530
I don't know. I don't!

00:48:01.704 --> 00:48:03.358
- Just give me a name.
- I swear to God.

00:48:03.532 --> 00:48:04.838
Give me a name!

00:48:05.839 --> 00:48:07.275
