right fucking now.

00:48:43.877 --> 00:48:47.098
Okay. Okay, just hold on.

00:48:47.272 --> 00:48:50.101
I hauled some supplies for 'em
a couple of months ago.

00:48:50.275 --> 00:48:52.190
